{"id":645495,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【旧闻重温】正午传真｜朱镕基香港讲话：假如香/","date":"2020-05-26T21:26:30Z","modified":"2020-05-27T07:48:53Z","title":"【旧闻重温】朱镕基香港讲话视频违规：假如香港在我们手里搞坏 我们岂不成了民族罪人","content":"<div class=\"kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">CDT编者按：本文朱镕基演讲（腾讯）视频已被删除。</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645496\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.15.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.15.png 618w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.15-300x233.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">2002年11月19日，时任中共总理的朱镕基，出席香港特区政府在礼宾府举行的欢迎晚宴。期间，他针对当时的香港局势，脱稿讲演了近半个小时。</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645497\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.26.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.26.png 611w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.26-300x241.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<p>香港经济当时陷入谷底，时任特首的董建华向访港的朱镕基求救，朱镕基在即兴演说中指出，香港的优势并没有丧失，竞争力和经济实力没有降低，香港完全可以凭藉自己的力量克服当前的困难。</p>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645499\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.35.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"379\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.35.png 612w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.35-300x227.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<p>朱镕基强调，作为中国一颗璀璨的明珠，香港是大有希望的，大有前途的，要寄希望于香港600多万人民，寄希望于香港的年轻一代……</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<p>他说，&#8221;我就不相信香港会搞不好，如果香港搞不好，不但港府官员有责任，北京中央政府也有责任，香港回归祖国，在我们手里搞坏，我们岂不成了民族罪人？不会的！&#8221;</p>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">演讲结束后，朱镕基走下台之时，突然高呼&#8221;我爱香港&#8221;，引起会场经久不息的掌声，也赢得香港各界的好评。</div>\n</div>\n<p>youtube视频备份：</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"重温朱镕基讲话 香港如果搞坏了，我们就是民族罪人\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vRzNz8RBfLo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<p>小编语：我也爱香港，我也爱中国，可是为个毛线，我仅仅发了一篇，人民愿意斗争到底，一个月30天，就给我封了22天，不过还好，腾讯比较人性，还有申诉之路，可是，申诉，申诉成功是不可能滴，就这么霸气！就这么膨胀仅用我了了三行字，解释一下，为何失踪这么久，亲们，我胡汉三又回来啦！你们久等了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645498\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.45.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.45.png 678w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/屏幕快照-2020-05-26-下午5.19.45-300x255.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">\n<div id=\"article-content\" class=\"content-floated-wrap fb-quotable __reader_view_article_wrap_12723210677115304__\">\n<div class=\"wsw\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/CDS%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B5%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\">CDS专页 | 香港抗争</a></strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案 |<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%B6\">一国两制</a></strong></p>\n</div>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,38912,38960],"tags":[12719,28126,9861,8712]}